verbs.description: Over the years , members of the Trump family [V: have] acquired some unexpected friendships . From Ivanka Trump and Chelsea Clinton to Donald Trump and Kanye West , these unlikely friendships came to light in the midst of one of the most divisive elections in history . And not all of them support ' The Donald . '
